column1: OK, I am not a professional movie critic but come on...a true story!!!

!

They are tunneling under another store to get underneath the bank and stumble across a tomb.

At tomb with a passageway which goes directly under the bank.

OK, I'll play along.

But then they get into the bank and decide to go to sleep.
I am sure with all the adrenaline pumping through them they are going to just fall asleep.

!

Glad I didn't have to pay to watch this one.
